{"tid":1298210,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"麻煩用社會信用評分呢個POINT叫醒身邊仲未醒既港豬","createTime":"2019-07-08T21:54:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T07:59:10.000Z","uid":58841,"like":106,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"19615686aa000b69314cbdc768dca12d613af457","tid":1298210,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T21:54:05.000Z","msg":"係香港，假設你做左以下行為可能會扣分<br />\n1.上連登<br />\n2.衝紅燈/亂過馬路<br />\n3.屌黑警<br />\n4.係街大聲屌鳩人<br />\n5.大聲講是非<br />\n6.周街泊車<br />\n7.穩瞞資產<br />\n<br />\n扣左分會點？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你無得買樓、無得裝修，無得搭車同去旅行<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n萬一過左好撚大獲"},{"pid":"ebde286384b8404718a4c37d9d02c0141918828b","tid":1298210,"uid":81273,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T21:55:45.000Z","msg":"有班撚屌人實會話冇得同共產黨鬥<br />\n你唔反政府 佢咪唔搞你"},{"pid":"c7e29dd23e1adbaae9c3ce4124e12aceb8218c8b","tid":1298210,"uid":138233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T21:57:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15fbda85e57f5e08398e0b6eb8c7c72ff693aba8","tid":1298210,"uid":138233,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ebde286384b8404718a4c37d9d02c0141918828b","tid":1298210,"uid":81273,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T21:55:45.000Z","msg":"有班撚屌人實會話冇得同共產黨鬥<br />\n你唔反政府 佢咪唔搞你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T21:57:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\